irst invested in snapdeal in  and continue to back them as they grow fuze formerly thinking phones networks bvp first invested in  and has continued to invest our independent and intellectually honest approach equips us to be thoughtful and trusted partners supporting founders through capital advice and introductions as their companies grow   track record our track record includes  ipos recently twilio mindbody flex pharma shopify box u and wix joined the ranks of bvp funded public companies yelp linkedin eloqua criteo and cornerstone on demand  along the way we’ve seen a number of our most exciting and innovative startups become part of something larger recent examples include periscope which sold to twitter before they launched twitch which was acquired by amazon for b and skybox imaging which was bought by google in  marking the first—and largest acquisition to date—in the new race for space   we invest wherever great companies are being built from seven offices around the world silicon valley middlefield road suite menlo park ca   san francisco brannan st suite san francisco ca  westchester palmer avenue suite larchmont ny   new york city madison avenue suite new york  ny  boston broadway nd floorcambridge ma  israel  hasadnaot streetseaview building a th floorherzliya pituachisrael   india vittal mallya road nd floorbangalore   india by the numbers  ipos b current fund  investment professionals business plans businessplansbvpcom press inquiries pressbvpcom website comments webmasterbvpcom download brand assets contact us  bessemer venture partners skip to main content aboutabout bvp strategies news blog contact companiesportfolio antiportfolio top exits find a career team strategiescloud computing consumer cyber security developer platforms financial services healthcare industry software infrastructure  marketplaces mobile space tech india opportunities israel opportunities video bvp thinking bvp funded search form search copy  bessemer venture partners all rig