ure partners from wikipedia the free encyclopedia jump to navigation search bessemer venture partners type private ownership industry venture capital founded  headquarters menlo park california united states website wwwbvpcom bessemer venture partners bvp is an american global venture capital firm founded in  the firm has  billion under management and operates offices in menlo park san francisco new york city boston israel and india contents  history  investments  geographies  references historyedit founded in  bessemer venture partners is the longeststanding venture capital practice in the united states bvp was originally formed as an offshoot of bessemer securities the family office of henry phipps a cofounder of carnegie steel in  bvp expanded its operations to india with the opening of an office in bangalore the firm’s investments in india include snapdeal and urbanclap in  bvp closed bvp vii a  billion fund with  million earmarked for investing in india in the same year the firm opened an office in israel the firm’s investments in israel include sisense wix nasdaq wix intucell acquired by cisco ravello acquired by oracle leaba acquired by cisco and traffix acquired by f among others in  bvp closed bvp viii a  billion fund that was its largest fund to date in  bvp closed bvp ix a  billion fund that the firm is currently investing as of  bvp has  partners investmentsedit bessemer venture partners invests in seed stage early stage and growth stage private companies the firm is primarily focused on investing in the following technology sectors enterprise consumer and healthcare bvp has helped build over  ipos and  ma transactions including yelp nyse yelp linkedin nyse lnkd twitch acquired by amazon dropcam acquired by google mindbody nasdaq mb shopify nyse shop twilio nyse twlo box nyse box ovascience nyse ovas and lifelock acquired by symantec geographiesedit bessemer venture partners is headquartered in menlo park with offices in san francisco new york city bosto