rd meetings took place in a padded room once used to demo loud set ups which ensured that those confidential conversations would not be overheard today that seems like ancient history yelp went public in  nyse yelp and now has active communities in  countries around the world  with more than  million rich local reviews yelp is the leading local guide for real wordofmouth on everything from boutiques and mechanics to restaurants and dentists   read more pinterest pinterest is a visual bookmarking tool that helps you discover and save creative ideas their mission is to help people discover the things they love and inspire them to go do those things in their daily lives  when bvp led the series a investment in  pinterest was just five people working—and sometimes sleeping—in a palo alto apartment that had seen better days  today more than  pinterest employees work in offices around the world  bessemer has supported the company at every stage   read more twilio inc twilio makes communication easy and powerful twilio is a communications platformasaservice providing infrastructure apis for developers and businesses to build scalable communication apps in the cloud  since it was founded in  over  web and mobile developers have used twilio’s cloudbased platform to integrate voice sms and mms capabilities into software applications  eager to help jeff lawson build the future of communications bessemer provided seed capital for twilio and has continued to back the company at every stage read more ovascience inc ovascience makes miracles happen founded in  with the goal of improving the treatment of infertility the company assembled a team of scientists physicians and advisers that are recognized leaders in the field of reproductive medicine in  baby zain rajani was born  zain was the first baby born with the assistance of ovasciences first product augment which increases the success of in vitro fertilization ivf and uses the mothers own cellular energy to revitalize her egg  